projects.name: Ride Share
projects.description: Developed a carpooling platform using React.js for the front end, Node.js for the back end, and MongoDB for the database. Implemented secure user authentication, ride booking, and profile management, emphasizing privacy and ease of use. Contributed to reducing urban congestion and carbon footprints through community-based ride-sharing.

projects.name: Pharmacy Management System
projects.description: Developed a Java-based web application for online medicine ordering and remote doctor consultations. Improved tracking of medication orders, patient histories, and communication between healthcare providers and patients. Focused on creating a user-friendly interface with robust data security, ensuring easy and safe access to patient information.

experiences.company_name: APSSDC (Andhra Pradesh State Skill Development Corporation)
experiences.description: Led the Screen Time Analysis project during an APSSDC (Andhra Pradesh State Skill Development Corporation) internship, using Python to uncover key trends. Conducted data analysis with advanced methodologies and industry-standard practices, improving decision-making and app comprehension.
